## 🧑‍💻 Getting Started

### ✅ Prerequisites

Make sure you have the following installed:

- [Go](https://go.dev/doc/install)
- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/)
- [ScyllaDB](https://www.scylladb.com/)
- [Docker (optional)](https://www.docker.com/) — for running Scylla or Postgres containers

---

## ⚙️ Backend Setup (Go)

1. Navigate to the backend folder:

```bash
cd backend

Install dependencies:

go mod tidy
Run the server:

go run main.go client.go

The server will run on http://localhost:8080.

 Usage
Sign in or log in through the login screen.

You’ll be placed on a tile-based map with your avatar.

Use arrow keys or WASD to move around.

When you’re adjacent to another player, a small chat box button appears.

Click the box to open a retro-style chat window.